{"tid":1849671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"救乜遮？ 根本都未有疫苗","createTime":"2020-01-29T07:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T08:16:37.000Z","uid":16925,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"987b42dd04613e1d912c3e5a00224e8c2a49578d","tid":1849671,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"律敦治講既「政府請客，醫護賣單」真係好中<br />\n<br />\n其實救乜遮，根本都未有疫苗，離開到武漢 既WARS病人都一樣會係香港死，實情就係比錢救唔到，但又迫住照顧佢地。黎到只係多個帶菌者黎香港，多左機會比前線醫護中招。<br />\n<br />\n光環就林鄭拎，命就醫護出，錢就黑警拎<br />\n<br />\n支特醫護前線有行動，罷工日去 Albert Road 吐口水"},{"pid":"7f1c3064cd1c83c3a16abc0cd1dfee5c5025b87b","tid":1849671,"uid":162015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fc377759f14f33797c89f2c4a18d49078f4b991","tid":1849671,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1c3064cd1c83c3a16abc0cd1dfee5c5025b87b","tid":1849671,"uid":162015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢地真心嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲廢老去到貼身既事就會發難渣嫁喇"},{"pid":"9f7d781d85b0c643568dc7adfae454349f998851","tid":1849671,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:35:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=9433f239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家